items.title: Is Bank Nifty getting ready for a new Bull run?
items.description: The combination of RBI’s rate cut, strong technical breakouts, and sector leadership puts banking stocks, particularly HDFC Bank and IDFC First Bank, in a sweet spot.

items.title: Chartist Talks: SBI Securities' Sudeep Shah still sees nearly 4% upside in Bank Nifty, bullish on these 4 stocks
items.description: Technically, all the moving averages and momentum-based indicators suggest strong bullish momentum in the Bank Nifty index. The daily RSI is quoting at 67.45, and it is in rising trajectory, which suggests strong bullish momentum.
